name: Knife
description: It is a tool or weapon with a cutting edge or blade, usually attached to a handle or hilt.

name: Peeler
description: It is a kitchen tool, a distinct type of kitchen knife, consisting of a metal blade with a slot with a sharp edge attached to a handle, used to remove the outer layer (the skin or peel) of some vegetables and fruits.

name: Wooden Spoon
description: It is a utensil commonly used in food preparation.
